{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT's responses are based on statistical patterns and may not fully capture the nuanced understanding of individual learners or their progress over time.",
    "Despite these limitations of ChatGPT, it is still possible to create meaningful prompts that offer some degree of content adaptation and customized feedback.",
    "We propose one such framework for looking at the different levels of PL from the perspective of its affordances based on current capabilities of technology.",
    "From the perspectives of the learning sciences, the key focus is about scaffolding the learner to practice, achieve and develop competencies in the process of learning.",
    "The one framework which has been most applied in understanding the mechanisms of scaffolding learning is the Zone of Proximal Development (ZPD) (Vygotsky, 1978)."
  ]
}